      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 14:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场因缺乏中国新一轮重大刺激措施而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/em-currency-traders-zero-in-on-us-election-driving-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国在备受关注的新闻发布会上未能公布进一步的重大刺激措施，新兴市场股市暴跌，引发人们对近期上涨行情的可持续性产生怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/em-currency-traders-zero-in-on-us-election-driving-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 涨幅达 14%，Mag Seven 股价上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的科技公司推动股市上涨，市场从一个月以来最糟糕的交易日中反弹。随着对美联储降息的预期稳定下来，美国国债的暴跌有所缓解。油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 22:34:30 GMT</pubDate>
